---
import Icon from './Icon.astro'
import Subscribe from './react/Subscribe.tsx'
import { footer } from '../../content/navigation.js'
---

<aside class="grid grid-flow-dense grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-[repeat(16,minmax(min-content,1fr))] grid-rows-[repeat(auto-fill,minmax(min-content,1fr))] gap-px col-start-container-start col-end-container-end shadow-placed rounded-lg lg:rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
  <Subscribe client:visible className="col-span-full lg:col-span-8 xl:col-span-7 row-span-10 bg-surface py-12 px-8 sm:px-12 sm:py-12 md:px-[5vmax] xl:py-16 xl:px-24" />

  <div class="@container/about col-span-full sm:col-span-8 xl:col-span-9 row-span-7 bg-surface py-12 px-8 sm:px-12 sm:py-12 xl:px-18 content-end dark:shadow-[-1px_1px_0_0_var(--color-surface-02)]">
    <h3 class="text-heading font-display font-variation-bold text-lg sm:text-3xl lowercase flex gap-2 mb-3">
      About the website
    </h3>
    <div class="flex flex-col @md:flex-row gap-x-6 gap-y-2">
      <p class="text-ui-body text-base flex-1">
        Hi, I&rsquo;m Steve McKinney, I write this small publication focusing on
        the design and build of websites. The aim is to bridge the gap
        between your design tool and code. And look at the craft behind
        creating websites.
      </p>
      <p class="text-ui-body text-base flex-1">
        This is a broad topic in itself, which feels challenging to achieve.
        But it remains a way to encourage self learning and sharing what I
        know&hellip;
        <a
          href="/about"
          class="font-semibold text-link hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200 ease"
        >continue reading</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-1 sm:col-span-8 lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-5 row-span-3 bg-surface py-12 px-8 sm:px-12 sm:py-12 xl:px-18 flex flex-col justify-end dark:shadow-[-1px_0_0_0_var(--color-surface-02)]">
    <h3 class="text-heading font-display font-variation-bold text-lg sm:text-3xl lowercase mb-4">
      Site
    </h3>
    <ul class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 sm:gap-y-4">
      {footer.map((link) => (
        <li>
          <a
            href={link.href}
            class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200"
          >
            <Icon icon={link.icon} size={link.size} variant="header" />
            {link.title}
          </a>
        </li>
      ))}
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-1 sm:col-span-8 lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-4 row-span-1 bg-surface py-8 sm:p-12 flex items-center justify-center dark:shadow-[-1px_1px_var(--color-surface-02)]">
    <a
      href="https://v7.iamsteve.me"
      class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200"
    >
      Old design
      <Icon icon="external" variant="header" size={16} />
    </a>
  </div>

  <div class="col-span-1 sm:col-span-8 lg:col-span-4 xl:col-span-4 row-span-2 bg-surface py-12 px-8 sm:px-12 sm:py-12 xl:px-18 flex flex-col justify-end dark:shadow-[-1px_0_var(--color-surface-02)]">
    <h3 class="text-heading font-display font-variation-bold text-lg sm:text-3xl lowercase mb-4">
      Elsewhere
    </h3>
    <ul class="flex flex-row flex-wrap gap-x-6 gap-y-2 sm:gap-y-4">
      <li>
        <a href="https://x.com/irsteve" class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200">
          <Icon icon="x" size={16} variant="header" /> x.com
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.figma.com/@stevemckinney" class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200">
          <Icon icon="figma" size={16} variant="header" /> Figma
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://github.com/stevemckinney" class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200">
          <Icon icon="github" size={16} variant="header" /> Github
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/steve-mckinney-5b5836102/" class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200">
          <Icon icon="linkedin" size={16} variant="header" /> Linkedin
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://mastodon.design/@steve" rel="me" class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 text-base font-ui lowercase text-body hover:text-link-hover transition duration-200">
          <Icon icon="mastodon" size={16} variant="header" /> Mastodon
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</aside>
